com.chatt.demo.custom

Class CustomActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.chatt.demo.custom.CustomActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Chat, Login, Register, UserList

    public class CustomActivity
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a common activity that all other activities of the app can extend to inherit the common behaviors like implementing a common interface that can be used in all child activities.
